### ============================================
### Reservation Service API (Port 8083)
### ============================================
### 예약 오케스트레이션 - Saga 패턴 구현
### 전체 예약 플로우: Flight -> Payment -> Ticket


### ------------------------------------------
### 예약 생성 (전체 플로우)
### ------------------------------------------

### 새 예약 생성 - 이코노미
POST http://localhost:8083/v1/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flightId": "KE001",
  "passengerName": "Kim Minsu",
  "passengerEmail": "minsu@example.com",
  "seatClass": "ECONOMY",
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "cardNumber": "4111111111111111"
}

###

### 새 예약 생성 - 비즈니스
POST http://localhost:8083/v1/reservations
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "flightId": "OZ456",
  "passengerName": "Lee Younghee",
  "passengerEmail": "younghee@example.com",
  "seatClass": "BUSINESS",
  "paymentMethod": "CREDIT_CARD",
  "cardNumber": "5500000000000004"
}


### ------------------------------------------
### 예약 조회
### ------------------------------------------

### 예약 상태 조회 (예약 ID로 조회)
GET http://localhost:8083/v1/reservations/RES-001
Accept: application/json

###

### 전체 예약 목록 조회
GET http://localhost:8083/v1/reservations
Accept: application/json


### ------------------------------------------
### 예약 취소 (보상 트랜잭션)
### ------------------------------------------

### 예약 취소 요청
POST http://localhost:8083/v1/reservations/RES-001/cancel
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "reason": "Customer request",
  "refundRequired": true
}
